WEBVTT

01:52.490 --> 01:57.370
[The Legend of Rosy Clouds]

01:58.630 --> 02:01.920
[Episode 29]

02:31.870 --> 02:33.730
Have the army proceed as planned.

02:33.960 --> 02:35.200
We'll go on ahead.

02:35.200 --> 02:35.920
Yes.

03:18.650 --> 03:19.510
Grandfather,

03:19.810 --> 03:20.560
this...

03:28.710 --> 03:29.660
Mayor Zheng,

03:30.760 --> 03:32.480
the governor isn't here.

03:32.800 --> 03:33.640
How about you

03:33.660 --> 03:35.710
go look in the estate's garden?

03:51.050 --> 03:52.140
Your Excellency.

04:02.270 --> 04:03.270
Your Excellency!

04:23.060 --> 04:25.060
Darn that brat Qi Zheng.

04:49.470 --> 04:50.440
Grandfather.

04:51.230 --> 04:52.000
No need.

04:52.520 --> 04:53.720
I'll get down myself.

04:55.210 --> 04:56.820
You're so skilled, Grandfather.

04:56.820 --> 04:59.220
Don't let the governor
get under your skin.

04:59.450 --> 05:00.590
Get under my skin?

05:00.860 --> 05:01.860
Who even is he?

05:05.280 --> 05:06.840
The governor refuses to show his face,

05:06.840 --> 05:08.640
making us run around his estate.

05:08.900 --> 05:11.170
He must be trying to show us who's boss.

05:11.200 --> 05:12.840
Show us who's boss?

05:12.910 --> 05:14.520
He doesn't even dare to show his face.

05:14.520 --> 05:16.440
Utterly pathetic.

05:19.240 --> 05:20.440
What brings you here?

05:22.550 --> 05:23.480
Second Brother!

05:26.150 --> 05:27.640
Zheng Shi, you're back.

05:35.710 --> 05:36.640
Granduncle Tao.

06:03.880 --> 06:06.080
Where have you been these past few days?

06:06.590 --> 06:08.190
It took you so long to return.

06:11.200 --> 06:13.530
I left Ling'an for some personal matters,

06:14.470 --> 06:15.930
and was delayed on the way.

06:17.210 --> 06:19.620
So the night my brother had his accident,

06:21.230 --> 06:22.920
you weren't by his side?

06:32.200 --> 06:33.080
Zheng Shi,

06:33.520 --> 06:34.560
do you know why

06:34.560 --> 06:37.159
Granduncle Yuan
suddenly committed treason?

06:38.390 --> 06:39.150
I only know that he'd

06:39.150 --> 06:41.680
been against
democratizing the selection exam

06:41.680 --> 06:45.280
and wanted to maintain
the old system of the Nine Noble Families.

06:46.760 --> 06:48.490
My brother sacrificed his life

06:48.830 --> 06:50.790
for the nobles of Jing City.

06:51.560 --> 06:52.730
Even if we don't

06:53.150 --> 06:56.270
carry on his will to abolish the exam,

06:57.230 --> 07:00.360
we can't let Jing City
be controlled by Ling'an anymore.

07:10.350 --> 07:11.950
Do you mean you want Jing City

07:13.130 --> 07:14.610
to become independent?

07:23.450 --> 07:24.780
What's wrong with that?

07:26.120 --> 07:28.180
It's not like we lack the capabilities.

07:28.180 --> 07:29.910
Why should we submit to others?

07:31.470 --> 07:33.230
Were it not for
concern of my elder brother,

07:33.230 --> 07:34.740
I'd have acted long ago.

07:35.000 --> 07:35.840
Zheng Shi.

07:38.790 --> 07:40.850
This matter concerns the survival of

07:41.590 --> 07:42.590
our Zheng family.

07:43.560 --> 07:44.590
So,

07:45.590 --> 07:48.000
we must stand united and fight together.

07:50.770 --> 07:51.560
Fight?

07:59.150 --> 08:00.750
You came to Ling'an this time

08:00.960 --> 08:02.440
prepared?

08:04.440 --> 08:06.320
I brought the army.

08:07.080 --> 08:08.710
Bringing troops into Ling'an

08:08.710 --> 08:10.040
is considered treason.

08:14.760 --> 08:16.710
This is just a preliminary test

08:16.710 --> 08:19.330
to gauge that brat Qi Zheng's limits.

08:22.350 --> 08:24.590
Grandfather only brought
20,000 troops this time,

08:24.590 --> 08:27.720
and they're stationed
outside the Ling'an checkpoint.

08:27.960 --> 08:29.500
It's just an act of posturing.

08:29.500 --> 08:31.170
No lines will be crossed.

08:37.580 --> 08:39.510
This Qi Zheng sure is infuriating.

08:43.960 --> 08:47.690
Are you sure those soldiers are
stationed outside the checkpoint?

08:52.710 --> 08:54.910
I'm afraid things outside have changed

08:55.160 --> 08:56.510
while you're in here.

08:57.710 --> 08:58.710
What do you mean?

09:01.040 --> 09:02.840
When I entered the city earlier,

09:04.440 --> 09:06.440
I didn't see a single Zheng soldier.

09:36.060 --> 09:37.390
You two really are here.

09:44.110 --> 09:44.750
Dad.

09:47.960 --> 09:48.960
Your Excellency.

09:49.920 --> 09:51.920
Why are you two sitting back to back?

09:54.560 --> 09:56.160
What's going on with you two?

09:56.860 --> 09:57.650
Not talking,

09:57.680 --> 09:59.410
not eating, and not going home?

10:00.680 --> 10:01.890
Yun.

10:02.350 --> 10:03.610
Listen, my daughter,

10:03.990 --> 10:05.000
this man

10:05.750 --> 10:07.400
is just the worst.

10:08.470 --> 10:09.870
Lord Fan Qi is even worse.

10:10.920 --> 10:12.330
He wants to eat my pet turtle.

10:12.330 --> 10:13.440
Your Excellency,

10:13.470 --> 10:15.900
how many times
do I have to explain it to you?

10:16.050 --> 10:17.200
Yours is a softshell turtle,

10:17.200 --> 10:19.310
an aggressive fish-like species,

10:19.590 --> 10:21.200
which can be eaten.

10:21.510 --> 10:23.080
It's my pet.

10:23.080 --> 10:23.990
I know very well if

10:23.990 --> 10:24.990
it's a softshell or not, OK?

10:24.990 --> 10:26.590
Well, living to my age,

10:26.590 --> 10:28.560
I know very well

10:28.560 --> 10:30.500
what can be eaten and what cannot.

10:30.570 --> 10:31.900
I doubt that's true now.

10:32.680 --> 10:34.010
Alright, stop arguing.

10:34.550 --> 10:37.500
So you two are fighting over this?

10:37.730 --> 10:39.460
-That is right!
-That is right!

10:41.110 --> 10:41.940
Sure.

10:42.340 --> 10:44.340
This matter is so important.

10:44.870 --> 10:46.420
More important than

10:46.560 --> 10:48.470
the 20,000 troops of Zheng's Army

10:48.470 --> 10:50.000
about to arrive in Ling'an.

10:55.470 --> 10:56.110
Wait...

11:00.590 --> 11:01.680
You both knew?

11:03.080 --> 11:04.080
Your Excellency.

11:04.400 --> 11:06.160
Right, right.

11:06.190 --> 11:08.100
Yours is a pet turtle.

11:09.680 --> 11:10.800
Take good care of it.

11:10.800 --> 11:14.000
Now there are 20,000
of them aggressive little bastards.

11:14.590 --> 11:16.180
I have something to do. Goodbye.

11:16.180 --> 11:16.770
You...

11:17.470 --> 11:18.630
20,000 of them!

11:20.280 --> 11:21.350
Dad! Dad!

11:21.750 --> 11:23.080
Aren't you going to eat?

11:29.110 --> 11:30.350
When did you find out?

11:33.750 --> 11:35.560
Why are there so many
unexpected obstacles along the way?

11:35.560 --> 11:36.440
I know.

11:51.850 --> 11:53.160
Keep battle formation!

11:53.160 --> 11:54.470
-Yes!
-Yes!

12:07.680 --> 12:08.630
Who's there?

12:14.350 --> 12:15.560
Who goes there?

12:16.300 --> 12:19.030
How dare you trespass
on the Ling'an checkpoint?

12:19.410 --> 12:20.620
My apologies!

12:20.650 --> 12:21.960
So it's Commander Wei.

12:22.680 --> 12:23.810
You misunderstood.

12:23.870 --> 12:25.100
We're merely escorting

12:25.100 --> 12:27.710
Mayor Zheng to the estate
to express his gratitude.

12:27.710 --> 12:29.770
We have no intention of trespassing.

12:30.250 --> 12:32.180
Commander Wei, please let us pass.

12:33.170 --> 12:34.970
This is the Ling'an checkpoint.

12:45.230 --> 12:46.250
We're at least

12:46.270 --> 12:47.800
15 miles away from the moat.

12:48.400 --> 12:50.110
It's clearly drawn here!

12:50.970 --> 12:52.370
The governor changed it.

12:53.800 --> 12:55.000
When did he change it?

12:57.710 --> 12:58.820
Right now.

13:17.980 --> 13:19.240
You haven't told me

13:19.360 --> 13:20.500
how you knew

13:20.520 --> 13:21.980
they'd bring troops here.

13:26.040 --> 13:26.800
No.

13:27.040 --> 13:28.440
No food until you tell me.

13:35.470 --> 13:36.280
Fine, fine.

13:37.080 --> 13:38.410
I'll eat after talking.

13:38.800 --> 13:39.690
Even though I

13:40.160 --> 13:41.450
kept the Zheng family

13:41.680 --> 13:42.870
out of the treason,

13:43.750 --> 13:45.680
Zheng Yuan was a traitor after all.

13:46.750 --> 13:48.950
If Jing City received an order right now

13:49.440 --> 13:51.300
to bring Zheng Yuan's ashes back,

13:52.110 --> 13:53.310
if you were Zheng Tao,

13:53.750 --> 13:54.750
what'd you think?

13:56.750 --> 13:57.740
First of all,

13:58.200 --> 14:00.130
I must have some doubts.
After all,

14:00.750 --> 14:03.230
one shouldn't disobey
Your Excellency's order.

14:03.230 --> 14:04.870
So...

14:07.080 --> 14:08.390
So they

14:08.990 --> 14:10.130
sent troops here to

14:10.400 --> 14:11.560
guard against you.

14:12.080 --> 14:12.940
Subsequently,

14:14.160 --> 14:15.630
I'll find an excuse

14:15.870 --> 14:17.280
to detain him in Ling'an.

14:18.200 --> 14:19.460
Then Jing City

14:19.870 --> 14:21.080
will be leaderless.

14:22.990 --> 14:24.590
If they also thought of this,

14:24.730 --> 14:26.080
they either wouldn't come,

14:26.080 --> 14:27.000
or they'd find

14:27.510 --> 14:29.170
someone else to come instead.

14:29.630 --> 14:31.160
If it were the old Zheng Tao,

14:31.280 --> 14:32.550
that's what he'd do.

14:32.990 --> 14:34.540
But Zheng Tao is currently

14:35.110 --> 14:36.810
the mayor of Jing City.

14:37.280 --> 14:38.350
If he didn't even dare come

14:38.350 --> 14:39.710
pick up Zheng Yuan's ashes,

14:39.710 --> 14:41.230
wouldn't it completely destroy

14:41.230 --> 14:42.890
his credibility in Jing City?

14:45.040 --> 14:46.900
Therefore, not only must he come,

14:47.160 --> 14:48.890
but he must come aggressively.

14:49.110 --> 14:50.350
If he returns in one piece,

14:50.350 --> 14:51.560
it'll awe everyone.

14:52.080 --> 14:53.000
If he does not,

14:53.470 --> 14:54.930
they'll rise up in revolt.

14:54.970 --> 14:55.580
Exactly.

14:57.080 --> 14:59.140
This is also what Elder Zheng thought

14:59.230 --> 15:01.490
is the best opportunity he earned for us.

15:07.800 --> 15:08.830
In any case,

15:09.350 --> 15:11.040
with 20,000 elite soldiers outside,

15:11.040 --> 15:12.570
we still have to be on guard.

15:15.080 --> 15:17.610
We need to come up
with a countermeasure soon.

15:22.320 --> 15:23.650
Or does Your Excellency

15:24.750 --> 15:26.550
already have it all thought out?

15:30.630 --> 15:32.760
Since the fish is already on the table,

15:32.870 --> 15:33.680
can't we just

15:34.010 --> 15:36.430
start eating it from wherever we want?

15:36.960 --> 15:37.560
Here.

15:38.400 --> 15:39.400
Try this.

16:04.040 --> 16:04.640
Excuse me.

16:04.900 --> 16:06.280
The Zhengs are in mourning.

16:06.280 --> 16:07.960
No one is allowed to enter.

16:09.110 --> 16:10.990
I heard Young Master Zheng Shi is back,

16:10.990 --> 16:11.990
so I came to visit.

16:12.560 --> 16:13.770
This is his order.

16:14.160 --> 16:15.400
Please go back, Miss.

16:16.510 --> 16:18.500
Please let him know I'm here, sir.

16:18.870 --> 16:20.200
Just say that I'm...

16:21.430 --> 16:22.630
Fan Yun from the Fan family,

16:22.630 --> 16:24.080
with something to discuss.

16:24.080 --> 16:25.280
Please go back, Miss.

18:03.640 --> 18:04.970
Young Master Zheng Shi.

18:05.120 --> 18:05.960
Fan Yun.

18:06.790 --> 18:07.720
Long time no see.

18:14.120 --> 18:15.450
Young Master Zheng Shi.

18:15.990 --> 18:17.590
Since we parted in Yong City,

18:17.680 --> 18:19.210
we haven't seen each other.

18:19.750 --> 18:20.910
You didn't even

18:21.550 --> 18:22.880
let me know you're back.

18:25.680 --> 18:26.510
How...

18:27.600 --> 18:28.600
have you been?

18:30.360 --> 18:31.890
Let's talk somewhere else.

18:37.750 --> 18:38.720
So much wine.

18:39.230 --> 18:41.160
It must cost a month of your salary.

18:42.710 --> 18:43.640
The last time

18:44.120 --> 18:46.580
you came to the private school
to look for me,

18:46.710 --> 18:48.310
you brought this exact wine.

18:56.840 --> 18:58.240
Have a few drinks with me.

18:58.880 --> 19:00.550
Tonight's moon is breathtaking,

19:00.550 --> 19:01.880
yet I'm drinking alone.

19:02.120 --> 19:03.230
How dreary.

19:05.230 --> 19:06.160
Fan Yun,

19:07.390 --> 19:09.250
can you play another piece for me?

19:16.980 --> 19:17.790
Sure.

20:31.750 --> 20:32.830
Thank you, Fan Yun.

20:43.710 --> 20:44.310
Cheers.

20:53.410 --> 20:54.610
I still remember that

20:55.600 --> 20:57.060
the first time I tried wine

20:58.560 --> 21:00.420
was the day my mother passed away.

21:04.030 --> 21:05.230
That night,

21:06.200 --> 21:07.640
my dad came home

21:08.310 --> 21:09.710
with a large jug of wine.

21:10.550 --> 21:11.790
He drank half of it

21:12.070 --> 21:12.960
and got drunk.

21:14.070 --> 21:14.970
I ran over,

21:15.400 --> 21:16.370
took a few sips,

21:16.920 --> 21:17.920
and got drunk too.

21:19.400 --> 21:20.200
But

21:21.470 --> 21:22.790
that night,

21:23.200 --> 21:25.130
I had a very, very beautiful dream.

21:26.960 --> 21:28.290
I dreamed that my mother

21:29.230 --> 21:30.630
came back to see me again.

21:41.550 --> 21:44.210
I'm worried Grandfather
won't enter my dreams.

21:45.120 --> 21:47.780
After all, I was neither
sensible nor obedient.

21:48.030 --> 21:49.560
I failed the selection exam

21:50.070 --> 21:51.920
and often made him mad.

21:53.310 --> 21:55.310
Maybe he never wants to see me again.

22:00.230 --> 22:01.160
That's not true.

22:01.990 --> 22:02.960
He just

22:03.530 --> 22:05.090
didn't want you to worry.

22:11.160 --> 22:13.160
When he knew our family
disrupted the exam

22:13.160 --> 22:14.360
to test him,

22:15.570 --> 22:17.030
he didn't want me to worry.

22:18.750 --> 22:20.450
When he felt weak and frail,

22:22.440 --> 22:24.300
he didn't want me to worry either.

22:25.990 --> 22:28.120
When he felt that our family situation
was out of control,

22:28.120 --> 22:29.550
worrying about the people,
the family—

22:29.550 --> 22:30.780
about everything—

22:33.470 --> 22:35.270
he still didn't want me to worry.

22:38.850 --> 22:41.710
He shouldered the weight
of the grand scheme alone,

22:42.610 --> 22:45.010
setting up a trap for Qi Zheng
with his life.

22:46.390 --> 22:47.860
♪ I could have ♪

22:47.890 --> 22:49.480
♪ Played every trick in the book ♪

22:49.160 --> 22:50.710
But in the end, as his grandson...

22:49.510 --> 22:52.870
♪ But I chose painstaking devotion ♪

22:53.050 --> 22:54.700
♪ Never caging my love ♪

22:54.730 --> 22:58.950
♪ Even if I had to
trudge through a thousand miles ♪

22:58.680 --> 22:59.840
Young Master Zheng Shi...

22:59.080 --> 23:03.150
♪ Henceforth, I shall wander the world,
plucking petals and holding the moon ♪

23:03.410 --> 23:06.730
♪ Listen to the wind and admire the moon
for days on end ♪

23:05.070 --> 23:06.530
Young Master Zheng Shi...

23:06.900 --> 23:12.830
♪ Accept that I'm not your happiness ♪

23:12.900 --> 23:15.620
♪ Let go of what's before me ♪

23:14.270 --> 23:15.640
Regardless of his merits and faults,

23:15.640 --> 23:19.600
♪ Consider this the best ending ♪

23:16.190 --> 23:17.120
Elder Zheng

23:18.710 --> 23:20.230
was a generation's hero.

23:19.720 --> 23:22.200
♪ I disdain everything
in the vast universe ♪

23:22.230 --> 23:26.580
♪ So why do I care for
a single glance from you? ♪

23:24.270 --> 23:25.310
My condolences.

23:26.610 --> 23:29.240
♪ Drinking a pot of the past ♪

23:29.260 --> 23:34.120
♪ I toast to my withering self
as the curtains fall ♪

23:34.150 --> 23:40.370
♪ And you don't know the reason why ♪

23:41.580 --> 23:43.160
I understand the reasoning.

23:41.700 --> 23:51.210
♪ And you don't know the reason why ♪

23:45.030 --> 23:46.710
But I can't help wondering;

23:47.600 --> 23:48.790
if I had been here,

23:49.470 --> 23:51.130
I'm sure I could've found a way

23:52.950 --> 23:55.350
where my grandfather wouldn't have to die.

24:05.120 --> 24:06.450
Young Master Zheng Shi.

24:06.920 --> 24:08.200
Actually, some things

24:09.070 --> 24:10.830
aren't as simple as we imagine.

24:12.640 --> 24:13.710
Some things

24:15.270 --> 24:16.760
can't be changed

24:17.310 --> 24:18.620
by one person alone.

24:23.680 --> 24:25.480
Are you speaking up for Qi Zheng?

24:28.510 --> 24:30.200
My grandfather died in his bedroom,

24:30.200 --> 24:31.400
right in front of him.

24:33.110 --> 24:33.970
Yet you're here

24:35.550 --> 24:37.410
asking me to be the bigger person,

24:39.200 --> 24:40.440
to be more forgiving?

24:41.230 --> 24:42.680
No, you're mistaken.

24:44.120 --> 24:45.270
I just don't want

24:46.600 --> 24:47.790
you to be too sad

24:48.470 --> 24:49.710
and hurting.

24:51.840 --> 24:52.510
OK.

24:54.230 --> 24:55.290
Then let me ask you:

24:56.600 --> 24:58.150
in what capacity are we

24:58.170 --> 24:59.700
having this conversation?

25:01.710 --> 25:03.120
As Zheng Shi and Fan Yun?

25:08.260 --> 25:11.300
Or as Second Young Master Zheng
and Lady Fan?

25:27.070 --> 25:28.200
Today,

25:30.070 --> 25:31.790
I'm your confidant Fan Yun.

25:35.440 --> 25:36.810
I simply hope that

25:36.990 --> 25:38.130
you can

25:38.510 --> 25:39.910
pull yourself together.

25:40.570 --> 25:42.290
Don't let down Elder Zheng's

25:43.570 --> 25:44.880
expectations of you.

25:50.900 --> 25:51.590
OK.

25:52.640 --> 25:53.570
I get it.

25:59.440 --> 26:00.070
Cheers.

26:02.120 --> 26:02.790
Cheers.

26:13.850 --> 26:16.590
[Huiyun Pavilion]

26:14.710 --> 26:15.750
Mayor Zheng, you came all the way

26:15.750 --> 26:17.310
to pay respects and give thanks.

26:17.310 --> 26:18.570
I'm deeply gratified.

26:18.950 --> 26:20.350
If there's nothing else,

26:20.360 --> 26:22.290
stay in Ling'an for a few more days.

26:24.840 --> 26:26.640
I wouldn't dare.

26:30.990 --> 26:32.720
My coming to Ling'an this time,

26:32.850 --> 26:33.960
apart from giving thanks,

26:33.960 --> 26:36.680
is actually to report something.

26:38.030 --> 26:38.710
Go ahead.

26:44.310 --> 26:46.120
Liu Mu, the gate commander of Jing City,

26:46.120 --> 26:47.730
unfortunately died in

26:47.810 --> 26:48.940
an accidental fire.

26:50.550 --> 26:51.280
Accidental?

26:53.600 --> 26:55.990
The specific cause of the fire
is still under investigation.

26:55.990 --> 26:57.380
Currently, it's speculated

26:57.380 --> 27:00.710
that Gate Cdr. Liu,
who slogged for Jing City day and night,

27:00.710 --> 27:03.080
was in deep sleep due to exhaustion,

27:03.270 --> 27:06.510
failing to notice that the charcoal brazier
in his home had tipped over.

27:06.510 --> 27:09.230
So, he passed away in his sleep.

27:09.600 --> 27:11.230
It's truly a pity.

27:12.360 --> 27:14.420
Why is this matter only reported now?

27:15.920 --> 27:17.990
Gate Cdr. Liu is an official
of Jing City after all.

27:17.990 --> 27:19.030
It was an accident,

27:19.030 --> 27:19.750
but...

27:20.510 --> 27:21.920
No matter what, he died within

27:21.920 --> 27:23.270
my Jing City territory.

27:23.270 --> 27:25.030
The Zhengs cannot shirk the blame.

27:25.030 --> 27:27.550
So we decided to
seek an audience with Your Excellency

27:27.550 --> 27:29.840
to report this matter,
and at the same time,

27:29.840 --> 27:31.080
ask for punishment.

27:39.920 --> 27:40.710
In that case,

27:41.510 --> 27:44.710
I'll accord Gate Cdr. Liu
a grand burial with full honors.

27:45.360 --> 27:46.870
It's just that now,

27:47.200 --> 27:49.760
Jing City is without a gate commander.

27:53.140 --> 27:56.260
A new gate commander is needed.

28:03.550 --> 28:04.900
So you're here for this.

28:05.970 --> 28:07.130
No wonder.

28:07.990 --> 28:08.930
Mayor Zheng,

28:09.230 --> 28:10.750
you brought tens of thousands
of your troops

28:10.750 --> 28:12.080
to lay siege to Ling'an.

28:12.400 --> 28:13.930
It seems you came prepared.

28:15.310 --> 28:17.370
You must be joking, Your Excellency.

28:18.070 --> 28:19.400
Before my departure,

28:19.400 --> 28:22.400
I heard there were many bandits
on the mountain roads.

28:22.510 --> 28:24.400
I had to take extra precautions.

28:25.200 --> 28:28.200
But my army was
brought to a complete standstill

28:28.200 --> 28:30.530
before even reaching Ling'an, wasn't it?

28:30.960 --> 28:32.990
You need so many accompanying troops?

28:32.990 --> 28:33.810
I'd say it's

28:34.160 --> 28:35.510
more than enough to take down

28:35.510 --> 28:36.640
the entire Ling'an.

28:40.200 --> 28:42.070
I wouldn't dare.

28:43.960 --> 28:45.750
I'm getting on in years,

28:45.750 --> 28:47.470
and my grandson is inexperienced.

28:47.470 --> 28:50.130
Our Zheng family just went through
a major event

28:50.360 --> 28:52.960
and can't withstand too much turmoil.

28:55.030 --> 28:58.230
The Zheng's Army has stayed
in the tiny Jing City for a long time.

28:58.230 --> 28:59.600
I thought I'd take this opportunity

28:59.600 --> 29:02.440
to let them come out and see the world.

29:02.840 --> 29:03.790
What,

29:04.840 --> 29:07.070
surely Your Excellency wouldn't

29:07.600 --> 29:09.060
disallow this, would you?

29:12.270 --> 29:13.470
Of course not.

29:14.840 --> 29:16.700
Actually, I think your troops are

29:17.440 --> 29:19.700
hardworking and commendable in spirit.

29:19.990 --> 29:21.530
I even wish my troops could

29:21.680 --> 29:23.340
learn a thing or two from them.

29:24.640 --> 29:25.500
How about this?

29:25.990 --> 29:27.030
Let the two armies

29:27.550 --> 29:28.810
have a friendly match.

29:29.200 --> 29:30.920
I'll get to properly witness

29:31.600 --> 29:33.310
how you train your troops.

29:36.070 --> 29:37.680
Your Excellency wants your Qi's Army

29:37.680 --> 29:39.170
and my Zheng's Army to undergo

29:39.170 --> 29:40.700
a joint ceremonial review?

29:42.960 --> 29:43.540
What,

29:44.160 --> 29:46.760
surely you wouldn't disallow this,
would you?

29:47.120 --> 29:48.030
I...

29:50.230 --> 29:51.560
wouldn't dare disobey.

30:01.270 --> 30:03.930
Granduncle Tao, did you
see the governor today?

30:04.990 --> 30:07.050
Grandfather did a great thing today.

30:08.600 --> 30:11.460
He actually wants to
play a war of attrition with me.

30:11.880 --> 30:14.410
Doesn't he know
how many battles I've fought?

30:17.840 --> 30:19.970
But listening to the governor's tone,

30:20.360 --> 30:22.030
how about we just drop the matter

30:22.030 --> 30:23.290
of the gate commander?

30:23.440 --> 30:24.480
Why should we?

30:30.750 --> 30:32.080
After the joint review,

30:32.680 --> 30:34.680
the entire Qi's Army and nobles in Ling'an

30:34.680 --> 30:37.200
will witness
how awe-inspiring our army is.

30:38.230 --> 30:39.430
By then, the position

30:40.400 --> 30:41.400
of gate commander

30:42.680 --> 30:44.300
will be in the bag.

30:46.400 --> 30:47.870
If there's nothing else,

30:48.270 --> 30:49.530
I'll return to my room.

30:51.600 --> 30:52.400
Hold on.

30:56.120 --> 30:57.030
Zheng Shi.

30:58.270 --> 31:00.870
Do you know where
my brother's clan leader ring

31:01.310 --> 31:02.490
might be kept?

31:15.360 --> 31:17.370
"Gone today, forgotten tomorrow," huh?

31:17.370 --> 31:19.210
Grandfather's body is not yet cold,

31:19.210 --> 31:21.340
and you're already coveting his ring.

31:39.750 --> 31:41.230
What are you saying?

31:42.470 --> 31:43.120
I merely

31:43.120 --> 31:45.320
want to keep it safe until the ascension

31:45.920 --> 31:47.400
of the next clan leader...

31:50.510 --> 31:52.510
Lest it falls into the wrong hands.

31:55.590 --> 31:56.840
I don't know.

31:57.920 --> 31:58.640
You don't?

32:02.010 --> 32:03.040
I really don't.

32:24.770 --> 32:26.460
Even the gate commander's death

32:26.460 --> 32:28.590
could be kept completely under wraps.

32:28.710 --> 32:29.790
Jing City is

32:29.790 --> 32:31.790
notoriously brutal for officials.

32:32.070 --> 32:33.160
Previous gate commanders

32:33.160 --> 32:34.470
all had to lower themselves

32:34.470 --> 32:36.000
and collude with the Zhengs

32:36.070 --> 32:38.070
in order to leave office unscathed.

32:38.310 --> 32:39.600
But Gate Cdr. Liu was

32:39.600 --> 32:41.230
famous for being upright.

32:41.230 --> 32:42.640
Since he arrived in Jing City,

32:42.640 --> 32:45.030
he was never once swayed by
the Zhengs' carrots and sticks.

32:45.030 --> 32:46.360
The conflict between them

32:46.360 --> 32:47.760
didn't start yesterday.

32:48.270 --> 32:50.400
So there's even more reason to suspect

32:50.750 --> 32:52.010
whether Liu Mu's death

32:52.710 --> 32:53.390
was really

32:54.470 --> 32:55.540
an accident or not.

32:56.600 --> 32:57.550
The clan leader election

32:57.550 --> 32:59.510
is a private matter for each family.

32:59.510 --> 33:01.200
Governors have never interfered.

33:01.200 --> 33:02.770
But every city's gate commander

33:02.770 --> 33:04.750
has been appointed by governors.

33:05.750 --> 33:08.040
This is to maintain a balance of power.

33:11.920 --> 33:12.990
Now, if Zheng Xian

33:13.640 --> 33:15.710
becomes gate commander as they wish,

33:16.750 --> 33:18.150
the clan leader position

33:18.310 --> 33:19.770
will virtually be theirs.

33:21.360 --> 33:24.090
They want to take over Jing City
in one fell swoop.

33:24.840 --> 33:26.440
Basically, he's establishing

33:26.440 --> 33:27.570
that Ling'an should

33:27.760 --> 33:29.620
stay out of Jing City's business.

33:30.960 --> 33:32.550
They've brought their troops here

33:32.550 --> 33:33.680
with big ambitions.

33:33.920 --> 33:35.450
We mustn't lower our guard.

33:36.730 --> 33:38.190
The upcoming joint review

33:38.550 --> 33:39.880
is especially crucial.

33:41.230 --> 33:44.360
Zheng's Army boasts
elite troops and strong horses,

33:44.360 --> 33:45.890
fighting with great valor.

33:46.030 --> 33:46.960
If

33:46.960 --> 33:48.600
we can outshine them

33:48.600 --> 33:49.730
at the joint review,

33:50.310 --> 33:53.120
such a blow to their reputation
will undermine them

33:53.120 --> 33:54.400
more than

33:54.400 --> 33:55.430
a bloody battle.

33:55.880 --> 33:57.470
As long as we dampen their spirit,

33:57.470 --> 33:58.750
no matter how big their army is,

33:58.750 --> 34:00.080
we have nothing to fear.

34:00.230 --> 34:01.840
By then, we will

34:02.600 --> 34:04.120
have the upper hand.

34:10.110 --> 34:10.909
No one knows me

34:11.630 --> 34:12.760
better than Fan Yun.

34:29.440 --> 34:30.760
The discipline of Zheng's Army

34:30.760 --> 34:32.159
is surprisingly strict,

34:32.510 --> 34:34.400
not inferior to our army at all.

34:35.030 --> 34:36.070
How'd you think they

34:36.070 --> 34:37.870
got their glorious reputation?

34:38.030 --> 34:38.780
However,

34:39.070 --> 34:40.670
they're facing us this time.

34:40.719 --> 34:42.030
When it comes to formations,

34:42.030 --> 34:43.560
the governor's the expert.

34:45.770 --> 34:47.239
Commander Wei, Lord Gao,

34:47.670 --> 34:49.010
we have a new discovery over there.

34:49.010 --> 34:49.940
Come take a look.

34:50.469 --> 34:51.070
Let's go.

36:01.490 --> 36:02.970
This is truly

36:04.070 --> 36:05.440
unbelievable.

36:06.370 --> 36:07.080
Yes.

36:07.520 --> 36:08.420
To think the Zhengs

36:08.420 --> 36:10.720
were secretly raising
a flock of crow soldiers.

36:10.720 --> 36:12.320
When we actually fight them,

36:12.320 --> 36:13.980
those crows will be a problem.

36:14.280 --> 36:16.590
With Zheng Tao and Zheng Xian
still in Ling'an,

36:16.590 --> 36:17.590
their hands are tied,

36:17.590 --> 36:18.670
so they won't act rashly.

36:18.670 --> 36:19.280
Well, go back

36:19.280 --> 36:20.990
and report this to the governor.

36:20.990 --> 36:22.390
I'll handle things here.

36:22.590 --> 36:23.880
Why should I go back?

36:24.920 --> 36:25.670
Why else?

36:26.320 --> 36:27.440
I know you're full of integrity

36:27.440 --> 36:29.440
and wholly devoted to government affairs.

36:29.440 --> 36:30.960
But women,

36:30.960 --> 36:31.800
sometimes,

36:32.320 --> 36:34.650
won't take the hint unless you reject her.

36:34.800 --> 36:35.920
Just for my sake,

36:36.630 --> 36:37.730
humor her.

36:38.190 --> 36:39.760
Lord Wei, actually I...

36:40.110 --> 36:41.190
If you lose a single hair,

36:41.190 --> 36:42.240
my precious sister will

36:42.240 --> 36:44.190
make me search for it with a lantern.

36:44.190 --> 36:46.110
I'd rather avoid any trouble.

36:47.890 --> 36:49.150
You're exaggerating.

37:09.850 --> 37:12.550
♪ Wind sheds rain like tears ♪

37:12.580 --> 37:13.790
♪ Over the whole town ♪

37:13.820 --> 37:16.320
♪ At the second our gazes meet ♪

37:16.460 --> 37:20.030
♪ Past memories roar one louder beat ♪

37:19.150 --> 37:20.680
Not an exaggeration at all.

37:21.280 --> 37:22.240
It really is you.

37:22.780 --> 37:25.250
♪ Perhaps hearts long to seek ♪

37:22.920 --> 37:23.850
Why are you here?

37:24.360 --> 37:25.240
Why didn't you two

37:25.240 --> 37:26.550
say goodbye before leaving?

37:25.280 --> 37:26.640
♪ Etch within our fingertips ♪

37:26.550 --> 37:28.320
You even went so far.
Good thing I have good legs.

37:26.660 --> 37:29.550
♪ Hear crisp footsteps echo clear ♪

37:29.580 --> 37:33.050
♪ Strike out
on a fearless dream's frontier ♪

37:30.670 --> 37:31.400
You mean

37:32.030 --> 37:33.890
the horse out there has good legs.

37:34.460 --> 37:37.800
♪ Though fleeting years rush
without delay ♪

37:37.670 --> 37:39.110
Don't find me a nuisance.

37:37.860 --> 37:40.890
♪ A wisp of softness
tints your brow each day ♪

37:39.110 --> 37:41.110
I heard you were
conducting reconnaissance.

37:40.910 --> 37:42.910
♪ Walk side by side with moon and sun ♪

37:41.110 --> 37:42.590
The wind is strong
in the mountains at night.

37:42.590 --> 37:44.070
I'll leave after
dropping off these clothes.

37:42.930 --> 37:46.050
♪ When all is said and all is done ♪

37:46.080 --> 37:48.080
♪ We'll ride the ups and downs ♪

37:48.100 --> 37:50.530
♪ When deep love dwells within our eyes ♪

37:49.760 --> 37:51.070
My sister,

37:50.770 --> 37:53.790
♪ Our burning longing never dies ♪

37:51.070 --> 37:52.070
can't you

37:52.590 --> 37:53.720
tone it down a little?

37:53.720 --> 37:54.840
Don't always be so eager.

37:53.920 --> 37:58.720
♪ Wander together through wind and frost ♪

37:58.550 --> 37:59.280
Fine.

37:58.750 --> 38:00.750
♪ Every dark night fades at last ♪

38:00.780 --> 38:03.300
♪ When fate resides within our sight ♪

38:01.240 --> 38:02.320
Miss Wei.

38:03.410 --> 38:08.100
♪ Gazing toward each other's
distant light ♪

38:04.150 --> 38:05.750
The front line is dangerous.

38:06.510 --> 38:06.990
Let me escort you ba...

38:06.990 --> 38:07.590
OK!

38:08.200 --> 38:11.620
♪ What do heaven and earth seek
but salvation in companionship? ♪

38:11.650 --> 38:13.800
♪ Don't let the sun down ♪

38:21.480 --> 38:22.810
You can head back now.

38:22.840 --> 38:24.900
Any further, and we'll be in Ling'an.

38:25.420 --> 38:26.750
Enemies can easily hide

38:26.780 --> 38:28.440
within the complex terrain here.

38:28.440 --> 38:29.790
It's almost dark.

38:30.030 --> 38:32.030
Let me escort you through this pass.

38:32.320 --> 38:33.800
If Gao Ran wasn't doing it for my sake,

38:33.800 --> 38:35.470
you'd be going back by yourself.

38:35.470 --> 38:36.800
Actually, there's no need.

38:36.800 --> 38:37.550
I'm a Wei.

38:37.550 --> 38:38.960
They wouldn't mess with me

38:38.960 --> 38:40.890
even if their lives depended on it.

38:40.950 --> 38:42.360
Gao Ran, why don't we

38:42.380 --> 38:43.490
just go back now?

38:43.520 --> 38:44.830
Leave her here by herself.

38:44.830 --> 38:46.890
But a hidden attack is the deadliest.

38:47.170 --> 38:48.750
They've been provoking us
these past few days,

38:48.750 --> 38:50.080
just to vex our spirits.

38:51.700 --> 38:52.700
Gao Ran is right.

38:53.720 --> 38:54.840
When you return in triumph,

38:54.840 --> 38:56.640
I'll make you some pastries, OK?

38:57.280 --> 38:59.010
You might as well make them for me.

38:59.010 --> 39:00.610
Gao Ran doesn't like sweets.

39:00.700 --> 39:01.370
Sure.

39:01.830 --> 39:03.960
Then I'll have to trouble you, Miss Wei.

39:03.960 --> 39:04.960
No trouble at all.

40:11.360 --> 40:12.090
Mayor Zheng.

40:14.190 --> 40:16.190
Does my army look neat?

40:17.760 --> 40:19.090
Your Excellency's army

40:19.720 --> 40:21.630
is certainly elite.

40:22.800 --> 40:25.330
But my Zheng's Army
is also battle-seasoned.

40:25.920 --> 40:28.320
Let the two armies spar,

40:29.720 --> 40:32.160
so my soldiers can witness the prowess

40:33.280 --> 40:34.600
of your Qi's Army.

40:36.550 --> 40:37.750
How on earth can

40:38.180 --> 40:40.180
the Jing City's army compare to

40:40.210 --> 40:41.470
the regular Qi's Army?

40:42.760 --> 40:43.350
Zhao,

40:43.960 --> 40:46.000
since he wants to witness it,

40:46.030 --> 40:48.840
we should show him
what we're really made of.

40:52.320 --> 40:53.740
I agree with Lord Lyu.

40:55.070 --> 40:57.000
How would Mayor Zheng like to spar?

40:57.670 --> 40:59.440
Formations are

41:00.110 --> 41:01.770
an essential military skill.

41:02.190 --> 41:04.070
Tactical flexibility on the battlefield

41:04.070 --> 41:06.000
is the only way to defeat the enemy.

41:06.400 --> 41:08.400
Otherwise, the soldiers
will be like loose sand,

41:08.400 --> 41:09.510
fighting individually.

41:09.510 --> 41:10.910
Why not give us a chance to

41:11.360 --> 41:13.420
study your formation tactics today?

41:14.840 --> 41:15.720
In that case,

41:16.800 --> 41:18.530
since you're a guest from afar,

41:19.360 --> 41:21.560
Zheng's Army will set up the formation,

41:21.970 --> 41:23.500
and Qi's Army will break it.

41:25.150 --> 41:26.240
What do you think?

41:27.110 --> 41:28.470
My intentions exactly.

41:29.190 --> 41:31.190
However, since it's
just a sparring session,

41:31.190 --> 41:34.190
please go easy, Your Excellency.

41:34.190 --> 41:35.450
Don't go all out

41:35.670 --> 41:38.590
and hurt my soldiers.

41:40.670 --> 41:41.670
Naturally.

41:43.720 --> 41:44.320
Please.

42:17.400 --> 42:19.590
The Zheng's Army is keen on formations.

42:19.590 --> 42:21.190
In tomorrow's joint review,

42:21.470 --> 42:23.670
they'll surely play their trump cards.

42:24.630 --> 42:26.030
The Long Snake formation

42:26.470 --> 42:27.530
is true to its name.

42:28.110 --> 42:29.670
if attacked at the middle,

42:30.070 --> 42:31.840
the two ends will connect,

42:31.840 --> 42:33.370
trapping the enemy inside.

42:34.280 --> 42:36.030
The only way to break it is to

42:36.920 --> 42:38.250
attack from both sides,

42:38.800 --> 42:40.660
cutting off the head and the tail.

43:02.280 --> 43:04.150
With the Long Snake broken,

43:04.710 --> 43:07.170
Zheng Tao will
bring out the Double Dragons.

43:07.430 --> 43:08.720
The two dragon heads

43:08.740 --> 43:10.340
are its sharpest elements.

43:10.920 --> 43:13.190
So we must avoid its sharp edges

43:13.980 --> 43:15.510
and attack its foundation.

43:57.020 --> 43:57.940
Next,

43:58.510 --> 44:00.030
Zheng Tao will move on to

44:00.050 --> 44:01.710
the Heaven & Earth Omniverse.

44:02.030 --> 44:04.170
It's indestructible
from top to bottom.

44:04.170 --> 44:05.970
Only the middle is its weakness.

44:06.960 --> 44:09.380
But these 3 formations
transition into each other

44:09.380 --> 44:10.580
flexibly and smoothly.

44:10.580 --> 44:11.600
This formation's weak middle

44:11.600 --> 44:14.400
is very likely to become
the advantage of the next.

44:15.110 --> 44:16.820
So those who don't grasp formations

44:16.820 --> 44:18.220
could get trapped inside

44:18.270 --> 44:19.400
and be annihilated.

44:20.510 --> 44:22.640
This aligns with the Daoist saying:

44:23.030 --> 44:24.960
"One begets Two, Two begets Three,

44:25.240 --> 44:26.760
and Three begets all things."

44:26.760 --> 44:28.890
The only way to break this formation is

44:29.510 --> 44:30.630
to attack here.

45:27.530 --> 45:30.540
Formations on the ground
can't stump Your Excellency,

45:30.540 --> 45:32.750
but I wonder how Your Excellency will

45:32.880 --> 45:34.610
counter formations in the sky.

45:40.770 --> 45:41.520
Lyu,

45:41.550 --> 45:42.510
should I...

45:42.530 --> 45:43.490
Just sit still

45:44.170 --> 45:45.160
and trust the governor.
